12 Create 3 input text boxes and a submit button. Apply the background color for all text boxes as pink using class selector and change the font color of the submit button
    using the id selector.
    
ANS. <html>
    
<head>
    
    <style>
        
      .c1
    {
       background-color:pink;
    }
    
       
    #id1
        {
            color:red;
        }
    
    </style>
    
</head>
    
<body>
         <b>
         <label>ENTER NAME<input class="c1" type="text"></label><br> 
         <br>
        <label>ENTER AGE<input class="c1" type="text"></label><br> 
          <br>    
        <label>ENTER CITY<input class="c1" type="text"></label><br>  
        <br>
        
          <input type="submit" id="id1" value="SUBMIT">     
         </b>      
<br> 
</body>
    
</html>
======================================================================================================================================================================

13 Create a group selector to set the padding (25px) of a division and a paragraph text.

ANS. <html>

<head>
    
    <style>
    
        div,p
        {
            padding: "25px";
        }
    
    </style>
    
</head>
    
<body>

      <div>MY NAME IS VISHAL</div>
    
      <p>Arijit Singh (born 25 April 1987) is an Indian playback singer.[6][4][2] He sings predominantly in Hindi and Bengali but has 
      also performed in various other Indian languages.[7][8] He is the recipient of a National Award and a record six Filmfare Awards.</p> 
    
</body>    
</html>
